{"title":"【082】CSS布局之显示属性3.0","slug":"hell0-world28","date":"2022-10-20T14:28:27.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:20:15.012Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world28.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                display    <br><br>display指定一个元素是否或如何显示","covers":["./by1.jpg","./by2.jpg","./by3.jpg"],"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>display</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"display-style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n<br><br>\ndisplay指定一个元素是否或如何显示<span id=\"more\"></span>。默认显示值为block:元素显示为块级元素,inline元素显示为行内元素,none隐藏元素,地消失了。<br><br>\n而visibility:hidden/visible(可见);则占地保留。这在应用javaScript动态控制元素和隐藏元素非常有用。<br><br>\n内联元素<br><br>\n链接元素：a <br><br>\n文本修饰元素:sub,sup,del,b,strong,i,em<br><br>\n拆行元素：br<br><br>\n图片元素：img<br><br>\n范围元素：span<br><br>\n输入框元素：input<br><br>\n表格元素:table<br><br>\n矢量图元素:SVG<br><br>\n内联框架：iframe <br><br>\n       每个html元素都有一个默认的显示值,元素类型不同，默认的显示值也不同<br><br>\n    <ul>\n        <li>语文</li>\n        <li>数学</li>\n        <li>英语</li>\n    </ul>\n    div>span>3*3回车\n    <div>\n        <span>\n        <a href=\"\">课程表</a>\n        <a href=\"\"></a>\n        <a href=\"\"></a>\n        </span>\n    </div><br><br>\n        通过样式可以改变元素类型。<br><br>\n        (div.imgbox#imgbox$>{Box $}+br+img)*3回车<br><br>\n        <div class=\"imgbox\" id=\"imgbox1\">\n            Box 1\n            <br>\n            <img src=\"./by1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150px\" height=\"150px\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"imgbox\" id=\"imgbox2\">\n            Box 2\n            <br>\n            <img src=\"./by2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150px\" height=\"150px\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"imgbox\" id=\"imgbox3\">\n            Box 3\n            <br>\n            <img src=\"./by3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150px\" height=\"150px\">\n        </div>\n        <br><br><br><br>\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[],"tags":[]}